title: Matt Birk on Scott Studwell's Retirement #92Noon
description: Matt Birk in studio with PA, sharing some stories and his relationship with Scott Studwell, who announced his retirement yesterday after more than 4 decades with the Vikings organization as a player and personnel scout.
